application_stages: Online application → Psychometric testing → Partner interview → Assessment centre
interview_experience: Two-stage process with HR/senior associate first, then partner interview. Focus on commercial awareness and M&A case study.
advice: Research firm's recent deals and practice discussing commercial issues. Prepare for case studies.

application_stages: Online application → Video interview → Final interview
interview_experience: 30-minute video interview with pre-recorded questions, then competency-based final interview.
advice: Use STAR method for competency questions and thoroughly research practice areas.

application_stages: Application → Online testing → Phone screening → Assessment centre
interview_experience: Assessment centre with group negotiation, individual presentation, and 3-partner panel interview.
advice: Be collaborative in group work while standing out. Know recent banking law changes.

application_stages: Online application → Watson Glaser test → Two interview rounds
interview_experience: Graduate recruitment interview followed by litigation partners discussing recent High Court cases.
advice: Stay current with court decisions and practice logical reasoning tests beforehand.

application_stages: Application → Psychometric testing → Group interview → Partner interview
interview_experience: Group case study on workplace relations, then partner interview on employment law focus.
advice: Understand IR reforms and Fair Work Act. Be ready to discuss post-COVID workplace trends.

application_stages: Online application → Video interview → Final interview
interview_experience: Technical issues in video round, but final interview went well covering M&A and ESG topics.
advice: Test technology beforehand and have backup internet for video interviews.

application_stages: Application → Online testing → Case study presentation → Final interview
interview_experience: Presented infrastructure project financing case study to panel with energy transition questions.
advice: Deep energy sector knowledge essential. Understand government renewable energy policy.

application_stages: Application → Reasoning tests → Partner interview
interview_experience: Challenging partner interview covering ACCC decisions and hypothetical merger analysis.
advice: Strong commercial awareness essential. Read AFR daily and know recent enforcement actions.

application_stages: Application → Psychometric testing → Technical interview → Culture fit interview
interview_experience: Technical tax law concepts tested, plus culture fit focusing on international collaboration.
advice: Demonstrate global perspective and language skills. International mindset valued highly.

application_stages: Application → SHL testing → Video interview → Assessment centre
interview_experience: Intensive assessment centre with group exercise, individual interview, and written regulatory task.
advice: Focus on listening and building on others' ideas in group work. Know securities law basics.

application_stages: Application → Aptitude testing → Phone screening → Final interview
interview_experience: Technical screening call followed by energy partners discussing renewable projects and regulation.
advice: Genuine sector interest required. Must understand policy landscape and regulatory challenges.

application_stages: Application → Online testing → Group interview → Partner meeting
interview_experience: Group property deal negotiation exercise, then informal partner discussion on career goals.
advice: Diverse backgrounds valued. Highlight non-legal experience showing commercial skills.

application_stages: Online application → Video interview → Assessment centre
interview_experience: Group exercise followed by partner interviews focusing on client service.
advice: Strong focus on practical commercial skills and client interaction.

application_stages: Application → Testing → Multiple interviews
interview_experience: Boutique firm culture with partner-level interaction throughout process.
advice: Research firm's high-profile clients and recent transactions thoroughly.

application_stages: Application → Interview → Practical assessment
interview_experience: Focus on practical legal skills and Melbourne market knowledge.
advice: Great training firm - emphasize willingness to learn and work across practice areas.

application_stages: Online application → Phone interview → Final interview
interview_experience: Relaxed atmosphere with emphasis on cultural fit and commercial awareness.
advice: Strong national firm with good work-life balance. Research local property market.

application_stages: Application → Video interview → Partner interview
interview_experience: Technical insurance law questions mixed with general commercial discussion.
advice: Solid mid-tier firm. Show genuine interest in insurance and risk management.

application_stages: Application → Group interview → Individual interview
interview_experience: Strong focus on employment law knowledge and workplace relations.
advice: Know recent Fair Work developments and be prepared for technical questions.

application_stages: Application → Written exercise → Panel interview
interview_experience: Government sector focus with questions on public policy and administrative law.
advice: Understand government sector work and public policy landscape.

application_stages: Application → Psychometric testing → Interview rounds
interview_experience: Two-stage interview process with strong emphasis on technical corporate law.
advice: Well-regarded corporate practice. Know recent M&A deals and corporate governance issues.

application_stages: Application → Phone screening → Face-to-face interview
interview_experience: Regional focus with questions about serving diverse client base.
advice: Good regional opportunities. Show flexibility and willingness to work across different areas.

application_stages: Application → Interview → Practical assessment
interview_experience: Focus on client service skills and understanding of personal injury law.
advice: Strong plaintiff firm. Show empathy for clients and understanding of compensation law.
